examples.en: She plays the role of a crooked lawyer.
He is perfect in the practice of crooked ways.
The road suddenly crooked to the left.
His lips curled into a crooked smile.
He crooked his finger at us and led us to the table.
examples.ru: Он поманил нас пальцем и подвёл к столу.

examples.en: Get the Mayor and his crooked cohorts out of City Hall!
examples.ru: Долой мэра и его грязных пособников!

examples.en: He was riding a crooked horse when he was took. (R. Boldrewood, Nevermore, 1892)
examples.ru: Когда его схватили, он ехал на краденой лошади.

examples.en: The shade on the lamp was slightly crooked.
